\[4 + \sqrt 5 \]

\[y = 4 + \sqrt 5 \]

\[{x^2} + {y^2} = 9 \Rightarrow \left[ \begin{gathered}

y = - \sqrt {9 - {x^2}} \hfill \\

\end{gathered} \right.\]

\[V = \pi \int_{ - 2}^2 {{{\left( {4 + \sqrt 5 - \sqrt {9 - {x^2}} } \right)}^2}dx} \approx 152,469\]

(đvtt)
